summary: Intro. Founder Stars I suppose I’ll be going first. Hello! My name is Stars and this little initiative is my brain child. I make...
body:
Intro. Founder Stars

I suppose I’ll be going first.

Hello! My name is Stars and this little initiative is my brain child. I make art and share it, as I suppose all members of TAO do, hahaa. I myself don’t have a style I stick to. I’m more of a doodler and simple photo editor by trade.

Doodle+edited photo.

Because my style varies, when it comes to commissions, at least for the time being, it is pay what you want.

If you ask for something complex I’ll probably put a fair minimum price on it before accepting the commission.

Some Previous commissions for reference:

Allrighty then, I think that’s everything.

blog.name: autonomy1
blog.title: Peter Percival-AUTONOMY
blog.description: Shades, nuances, scraps of existence......looking directly at an object can sometimes be a meaningless, even a destructive use of time…in society we are trained to look at things quickly, process that information and move on to another view…so much information and meaning can be lost in the action of moving on….by changing the expected angle of view, or re-arranging elements of an image one can derive another meaning from it, and if not an absolute meaning an abstract one which makes us look once again…that is all one can ask for, another look…(©) Pete Percival - 2013 All Rights Reserved. Reproduction of any kind is illegal.
